FuncDef: The undo ipv6 redirect command cancels the configuration.
ExtraInfo:
Usage Scenario
A traffic behavior supports only one redirect configuration. Before configuring a new redirect command, delete the existing redirect configuration.
The undo ipv6 redirect command can be used to delete the redirect configuration.
